{"tid":1674964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如搞個每周黃店精選","createTime":"2019-10-25T14:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T15:05:25.000Z","uid":188393,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"244fc0246d2f11274ddfb60c650df2c7210f9e3a","tid":1674964,"uid":188393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:10:07.000Z","msg":"我見大家好似來來去去都係去果幾間黃店 其實黃店有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇必要集中幾間 而且條龍咁長要入去食到都唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁不如我哋每星期搵幾間精選去幫襯 最好分散每區 等大家都有機會幫襯 又唔洗排咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於邊幾間就要靠大家input 基本上深黃就推介左先 淺黃次之 鼓勵大家愈變愈黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連燈師點睇～"},{"pid":"18c765326b3fb078b83dfe019b686a0ce6f0a3b5","tid":1674964,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得OK<br />\n淨係食嗰幾間其實唔係咁好"},{"pid":"3ff353f0edced0bdb1328c0a5168e868484d3d71","tid":1674964,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"係 精選一下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27673ee150f2a1ddd8c54c1a212f2763687a2298","tid":1674964,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有效分佈購買力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a8d055bcd69de820f1983cf8f8d02e65e8f550","tid":1674964,"uid":229920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔錯 介紹多啲唔出名嘅黃店"},{"pid":"7b060a0dc40b5b111de7f47469d886641ce6e064","tid":1674964,"uid":254802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"可以既話分埋區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方便大家"},{"pid":"bc1964d786574a43938b42ab0280f990d5522322","tid":1674964,"u